channel.title: [525 on a mac] Permission Denied when running Java
channel.description: Today, when I went on my awesome Mac Mini and tried to set up a 525 RSPS and when I when to run it, it gave me "permission denied" on all the files. Could either someone tell me the problem or tell me how to port forward 43594 through virtualbox? I tried using sudo also when running the command.

item.title: [525 on a mac] Permission Denied when running Java
item.dc:creator: @gggccc gggccc
item.description:

Notice the word MAC there. You can’t do run as admin. I am on the only account on my computer.
